Invoke lambda functions within your DB instance
allows you to process data events from within a database
supported for RDS for PostgreSQL and Aurora MySQL
Must allow outbound traffic to your Lambda Function from within your DB instance
DB instance must have the required permissions to invoke the lambda functions (proper IAM policies)

---------------

RDS Event notifications

Notifications that tells information about the DB instance itself
you dont have any information about the data itself
Subscrib to the following event categories: DB instance, Snapshot, Parameter group, security groups, proxy, custom engine version
Near real-time events
send notifications to SNS or subscribe to events using EVentBridge

